</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>point</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Coordinates of the mouse at the moment of help event emission. </para>
</parameterdescription>
